org.scoverage.plugin

Class SCoverageReportMojo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.maven.plugin.AbstractMojo
      • org.scoverage.plugin.SCoverageReportMojo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.maven.plugin.ContextEnabled, org.apache.maven.plugin.Mojo, org.apache.maven.reporting.MavenReport
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SCoverageIntegrationReportMojo, SCoverageReportOnlyMojo

    @Mojo(name="report",
      threadSafe=false)
 @Execute(lifecycle="scoverage",
         phase=TEST)
public class SCoverageReportMojo
extends org.apache.maven.plugin.AbstractMojo
implements org.apache.maven.reporting.MavenReport
    Generates code coverage by unit tests report in forked scoverage life cycle.

    In forked scoverage life cycle project is compiled with SCoverage instrumentation and unit tests are executed before report generation.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Grzegorz Slowikowski
